definitions.definition: Any plant in the genus Solanum .
A traditional green vegetable in the genus Solanum , specifically Solanum nigrum , and sometimes Solanum macrocarpon , Solanum scabrum , and Solanum villosum .

main_definition: ( botany ) Any plant in the genus Solanum .
secondary_definitions: ( East Africa ) A traditional green vegetable in the genus Solanum , specifically Solanum nigrum , and sometimes Solanum macrocarpon , Solanum scabrum , and Solanum villosum .
